Description: Coder Desktop for Linux — Remote development workspace manager
 Coder Desktop provides a native Linux desktop experience for managing
 Coder remote development workspaces. Features include:
 .
  * Built-in VPN tunnel for seamless workspace connectivity
  * System tray integration for quick workspace access
  * Workspace lifecycle management (start, stop, rebuild)
  * Data Loss Prevention compositor for secure environments
  * Native credential storage via libsecret
